  "detailed_description": "You are a little witch from the big city who has just lost their job. Life didn’t go as you expected but now you can start anew on a tiny island full of possibilities! Grow your own magical garden, decorate your ancient tree house, care for cute creatures, and make friends along the way. Cook delicious new recipes using homegrown ingredients and be part of a wonderful community working together to make it thrive!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow Your Garden</h2> Transform an old dead monoculture into a thriving, diverse magical garden.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/c1792cf590cb1d2ea0d44c073a44601b.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mental Balance</h2> Be a positive influence on your surroundings and yourself. As you settle into your new life and get to know the people around you, they will gradually open up to you.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/4a43bbed99128e85e32cf357c8744c39.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook and Enjoy</h2>Discover and cook delicious unique recipes from all around the world in your magical cauldron for you and your friends to enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/416ff39885405bbeb09e724dc33ab562.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate</h2>Express yourself by decorating your place with your own creations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/3fc84062a839e5849561bcc5126e007c.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create a Community</h2>Befriend villagers and help to bring back the spirit of community.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/3df0febd65149e60fe06136c639d4e8f.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover Mysteries</h2>The island is full of secrets, hidden passageways and ancient texts. Investigate the past of a broken world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/b9eeee45eebf1633214d921b07aea78c.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Skills and Tools</h2>You grow with time and so do your skills and tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/81b0c79c7dd16498442eb8fb5374c418.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pet All The Animals</h2>Yes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/24647deb2aa8ee6a71a0c06aff8847c9.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "You are a little witch from the big city who has just lost their job. Life didn’t go as you expected but now you can start anew on a tiny island full of possibilities! Grow your own magical garden, decorate your ancient tree house, care for cute creatures, and make friends along the way. Cook delicious new recipes using homegrown ingredients and be part of a wonderful community working together to make it thrive!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow Your Garden</h2> Transform an old dead monoculture into a thriving, diverse magical garden.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/c1792cf590cb1d2ea0d44c073a44601b.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mental Balance</h2> Be a positive influence on your surroundings and yourself. As you settle into your new life and get to know the people around you, they will gradually open up to you.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/4a43bbed99128e85e32cf357c8744c39.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook and Enjoy</h2>Discover and cook delicious unique recipes from all around the world in your magical cauldron for you and your friends to enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/416ff39885405bbeb09e724dc33ab562.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate</h2>Express yourself by decorating your place with your own creations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/3fc84062a839e5849561bcc5126e007c.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create a Community</h2>Befriend villagers and help to bring back the spirit of community.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/3df0febd65149e60fe06136c639d4e8f.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover Mysteries</h2>The island is full of secrets, hidden passageways and ancient texts. Investigate the past of a broken world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/b9eeee45eebf1633214d921b07aea78c.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Skills and Tools</h2>You grow with time and so do your skills and tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/81b0c79c7dd16498442eb8fb5374c418.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pet All The Animals</h2>Yes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1240450/extras/24647deb2aa8ee6a71a0c06aff8847c9.avif?t=1751536853\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
